{
  "texts": [
    "Following this, the language identification phase excluded non-English documents by categorizing them based on the language of their tokens.",
    "Subsequently, the pipeline further refines the data through Documentwise domain-based filtering, narrowing down to 100 billion tokens pertinent to the financial domain by excluding 55B-token non-financial documents.",
    "Recognizing the importance of data privacy and relevance, the pipeline incorporates removing sensitive information, which is done using a classifier built using FinBERT (Araci, 2019).",
    "Line-wise corrections enhance accuracy and filter out 5B tokens of sensitive information.",
    "An extensive Fuzzy deduplication process reduces the data to 38 billion tokens."
  ]
}